{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">50 choices in the adventure will test your true personality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a Paladin who protects the weak, or a cold and selfish assassin for hire?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover your exact personality type through the Alignment chart and Personality Tags.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/PersonalitygifEN.gif?t=1732779426\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players utilize slashing as a core mechanic to disable monster attacks and to solve certain puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/KillerVisionDemo_2.gif?t=1732779426\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your choices shape the story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your decisions may not only result in the deaths of certain key characters but also lead to your demise by being crushed by boulders, Earth's gravity, assassination, or being eaten alive, among other possibilities...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/Rock.gif?t=1732779426\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Returning to the golden age of 90s video games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Apocalypse Sacrifice is a blend of 90s retro style and modern game design. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Its classic adventure gameplay allows you to experience nostalgic emotions while also providing a fresh gaming experience </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/\u9ed1\u57ce\u5821_\u5200\u5200.gif?t=1732779426\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2003 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse scenes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From forests to deserts, from modern buildings to ancient ruins, from the future to the past. <br>Travel across different times and spaces.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adventurers should always keep adventuring! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/Scene.gif?t=1732779426\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Digging for the truth </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carefully read NPC dialogues, gather items, documents, and records scattered throughout the world, and piece together the truth. Don't let any one-sided statements influence your judgment!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Release","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/741b5c53950c1ed34707b54823f2cbe164b7583f.jpg"},{"name":"Joe\u2019s Moneymaking Dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/b995dfab5baf570758c92b0b2f76546c9aa1d58f.jpg"},{"name":"A Mysterious Stone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/b0efd52fcf317abfa9434f0c7cb7aa31916361e4.jpg"},{"name":"Oni's Past","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/3f813d3a8df2d726a4194eac51b109165cd555ac.jpg"},{"name":"The Stone Statue's Origin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/8460f4b33be47c84439f21d59a1f1f00e837614b.jpg"},{"name":"Fishing Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/7d79d3a4b22c6f6993b81f45dc30b658baa94651.jpg"},{"name":"The Meaning of Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776600/424da8256bf0a26e9d9b95f9807162ef4fe8203d